OL,6,FThe escalating situation means the
OL,7,FA259 King's Road, between the Aquarium
OL,8,Froundabout and East Street, has been
OL,9,Fclosed because of the risk to public
OL,10,Fsafety.
OL,12,FWork will now get underway with
OL,13,Fcontractors, and the hotel's owner
OL,14,FBritannia to demolish the 200-year old
OL,15,F219-bed hotel.
OL,17,FThe fire on 15th July 2023 prompted a
OL,18,Flarge emergency services response with
OL,19,Fan investigation by East Sussex Fire
OL,20,Fand Rescue revealing a discarded
OL,21,Fcigarette was to blame.
