OL,6,FCouncillor Trevor Muten, Cabinet
OL,7,Fmember for Transport, Parking and
OL,8,FPublic Realm said, "While this will
OL,9,Fcause major disruption in the city
OL,10,Fcentre, public safety is our biggest
OL,11,Fpriority so it's vital we do
OL,12,Feverything we can to minimise any risk.
OL,14,F"The responsibility for making the
OL,15,Fstructure safe, informing affected
OL,16,Fresidents and businesses, and the cost
OL,17,Fis with Brittania, but the council
OL,18,Fwill be overseeing the work to ensure
OL,19,Fsafety of the public.
